commit_message: Update README.md with latest sample input and output

Changes test-input file

The earlier test-input file contained a funny error, where the second
column had a bunch of values that were copied from the first column.
The latest test input file fixes this issue.

Bugfixes to default options for --mixture and --output-file

The earlier version recognized the "lognormal" default mixture as "l",
because the default argument was declared as a string instead of a list.
The earlier version also did not correctly specify the output file
name when the --output-file/-o option is not specified.
Adds shortened options to command line interface of cpiEm

Update README.md

Reflects the argparse based command line interface in cpiEm.py

Adds argparse based command line interface to cpiEm

This version requires the argparse module to be available.
This version is untested though i.e. I need to ensure that its
results match up with whatever is in the submitted paper.

Update README.md

Skeletal README.md page created.

Adds cpiEm.py and test-input

cpiEm.py is the script containing the code for the CPI-EM algorithm.
test-input is a a two-column test input file for cpiEm.py
